Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for qualification have been published by department full form for Secondary School Teacher Eligibility Test vacancies in Odisha. If you are searching for a government job in Odisha then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies on the Secondary School Teacher Eligibility Test, from the starting date, and till the last date. If you are interested in all these vacancies in location and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about the application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Secondary School Teacher Eligibility Test in OSSTET, your Graduation must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The last date to apply in these posts is Available Soon

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35 years old. 

OSSTET Secondary School Teacher Eligibility Test Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

Detailed vacancies:

How to apply for OSSTET Secondary School Teacher Eligibility Test Recruitment 2021? 

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Secondary School Teacher Eligibility Test. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of OSSTET and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by OSSTET.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
